'''郵鎮'''（'''post town'''）是[[英國|英國]]郵編系統中最基本的單位之一。 <ref name=royal_mail>Royal Mail, ''Address Management Guide,'' (2004)</ref> 郵鎮填寫正確與否直接決定了郵件能否順利送達。現在其主要作用是區分沒有[[郵編|郵編]]的地點或街道。<ref name="code 2004">{{ cite web | url=http://www.psc.gov.uk/postcomm/live/policy-and-consultations/consultations/postcode-address-file--changing-postal-addresses/PAFCodeofPracticeReviewFinalDoc.pdf | publisher=[[Postcomm|Postcomm]] | date=March 2004 | script-title=en:REVIEW OF ROYAL MAIL’S LICENCE CONDITION 20 – POSTCODE ADDRESS FILE CODE OF PRACTICE: A DECISION DOCUMENT | accessdate=2009-12-13 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720050043/http://www.psc.gov.uk/postcomm/live/policy-and-consultations/consultations/postcode-address-file--changing-postal-addresses/PAFCodeofPracticeReviewFinalDoc.pdf | archivedate=2011-07-20 }}</ref>

==組織==
英國現有大約1,500個郵鎮，由[[皇家郵政|皇家郵政]]統一管理。<ref name="code 2004"/> 每一個郵鎮對應一個或多個郵區，涵蓋城市、小鎮及村莊。一般與行政邊界並不重疊而是取決於實際情況，因此常常跨[[英國的郡|郡]]、[[英國國會選區|國會選區]]和[[教區|教區]]。這也是原來英國的[[郵郡|郵郡]]漸漸廢棄的緣故之一。<ref name=pem>{{cite web |url=http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200809/cmhansrd/cm090623/halltext/90623h0008.htm |title=Pembrokeshire (Royal Mail Database) c218WH |accessdate=2009-07-23 |work=Hansard |date=2009-06-23 |archive-date=2009-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090625185008/http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200809/cmhansrd/cm090623/halltext/90623h0008.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>另外一些地區，一個postal district有多個郵鎮。

==用法==
皇家郵政規定郵件上必須填寫郵鎮，并儘可能採用大寫。但實際上小寫形式也被接受，有些地區更是慣用小寫。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.royalmail.com/delivery/mail-advice/addressing-your-mail | title=Addressing your mail | publisher=Royal Mail | accessdate=2012-10-25 | archive-date=2012-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108050055/http://www.royalmail.com/delivery/mail-advice/addressing-your-mail | dead-url=no }}</ref>

